{"prompt": "Generate a website for a professional law firm. The website should be clean and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Sterling & Stone Law Firm</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #b22222; /* Firebrick red */\n            --secondary-color: #f5f5dc; /* Beige */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --light-text-color: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            margin: 5px 0;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        nav ul {\n            list-style: none;\n            padding: 0;\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li {\n            display: inline;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a {\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav ul li a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        section {\n            padding: 40px 0;\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(178, 34, 34, 0.7), rgba(178, 34, 34, 0.7)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x500/b22222/ffffff?text=Law+Firm+Image') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 0;\n            box-shadow: inset 0 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            text-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);\n        }\n\n        .section-title {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            position: relative;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .section-title::after {\n            content: '';\n            position: absolute;\n            left: 50%;\n            bottom: 0;\n            transform: translateX(-50%);\n            width: 60px;\n            height: 3px;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .card {\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n            border: 1px solid #ddd;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 25px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .card h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-top: 0;\n        }\n\n        .card p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info {\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info p {\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info strong {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        #contact-form {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        #contact-form input,\n        #contact-form textarea {\n            width: 80%;\n            max-width: 500px;\n            padding: 12px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        #contact-form button {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        #contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #9a1d1d; /* Darker red */\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Sterling & Stone Law Firm</h1>\n            <p>Your Trusted Legal Counsel</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <ul>\n                <li><a href=\"#about\">About Us</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#services\">Services</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#attorneys\">Our Attorneys</a></li>\n                <li><a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a></li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </nav>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Justice, Diligence, and Excellence.</h2>\n            <p>Dedicated to protecting your rights and achieving your goals.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">About Sterling & Stone</h2>\n            <p>Sterling & Stone is a premier law firm committed to providing exceptional legal representation across a wide range of practice areas. With decades of combined experience, our attorneys are passionate about delivering strategic, effective, and client-focused solutions. We believe in building strong relationships based on trust, integrity, and a deep understanding of our clients' needs.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"services\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">Our Services</h2>\n            <div class=\"card-grid\">\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Corporate Law</h3>\n                    <p>Navigating complex business challenges with expert legal advice.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Litigation</h3>\n                    <p>Aggressive and strategic representation in civil and commercial disputes.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Real Estate Law</h3>\n                    <p>Secure and efficient handling of all your property transactions.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Estate Planning</h3>\n                    <p>Protecting your legacy and ensuring your wishes are met.</p>\n                </div>\n                 <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Family Law</h3>\n                    <p>Compassionate and skilled guidance through sensitive family matters.</p>\n                </div>\n                 <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Intellectual Property</h3>\n                    <p>Safeguarding your innovations and creative works.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n     <section id=\"attorneys\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">Meet Our Attorneys</h2>\n            <div class=\"card-grid\">\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Eleanor Sterling</h3>\n                    <p>Senior Partner, Corporate & Litigation</p>\n                    <p><i>\"Excellence in every case.\"</i></p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Marcus Stone</h3>\n                    <p>Managing Partner, Real Estate & Estate Planning</p>\n                    <p><i>\"Securing your future, today.\"</i></p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"card\">\n                    <h3>Sophia Chen</h3>\n                    <p>Associate Attorney, Family & IP Law</p>\n                    <p><i>\"Dedicated to compassionate advocacy.\"</i></p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">Get In Touch</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <p>We are here to help. Contact us today for a consultation.</p>\n                <p><strong>Phone:</strong> (123) 456-7890</p>\n                <p><strong>Email:</strong> info@sterlingstonelaw.com</p>\n                <p><strong>Address:</strong> 123 Justice Avenue, Suite 100, Metropolis, CA 90210</p>\n            </div>\n            <form id=\"contact-form\">\n                <input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <input type=\"tel\" placeholder=\"Your Phone Number\">\n                <textarea placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"5\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Sterling & Stone Law Firm. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Disclaimer: The information on this website is for informational purposes only and does not constitute legal advice.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n    <style>\n        .card-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 20px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}